column1: # For annotating ICES region based on FDIR hovedområde
# Hovedområde area codes used by the Norwegian Directorate of Fisheries.
# ICESlowestmatchingsubdivision is the lowest ICES subdivision that can be matched at least partially by combinations of FDIR hovedområde
# ICESlowestsubdivision is the lowest subdivision of the ICES regions that overlaps with the other two columns.
